\cf0 align text left  -- command-shift-left bracket\
align text right  -- command-shift-right bracket\
center text - command-shift-backslash\
underline -- command-u\
bold -- command-b\
italic -- command-i\
\
ALWAYS remember that only the selected text will be effected by the change in formatting! If you use these commands when nothing is selected, everything that is typed at that point in the document will be effected by this formatting.\
